{"title":"镰刀和铁锤","authors":["贺海涛"],"dates":[{"year":1989,"month":12,"day":4}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"镰刀和铁锤"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"贺海涛"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我喜欢镰刀和铁锤"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——最朴素的美"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"镰刀收获成熟"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"铁锤坚实意志"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"当它们举在一起"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"放射正义的光辉"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"使我们的激情趋于崇高"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在迷乱的云中清醒"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一种坚定的信念"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"充实并渗透我们的胸怀"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"红通通的布上"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"金黄的镰刀和铁锤"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}